      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m so happy!!!&lt;br&gt;
I finally figured out how to get VSCode to build and push new changes of my Hugo website to Neocities automatically.&lt;br&gt;
This problem took me so long to solve (with a lot of experimentation) because all the tools I found were far too technical for a n00b like me.&lt;/p&gt;
